 3640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3564, \"end\": 3573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031347434765, \"rank\": 9.687464026184058e-05, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it made me so sad.\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And someone said, 'You should not be sad.\", \"from\": 3664, \"to\": 3705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You should be mad about it.'\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am like, 'Trust me.\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It makes me mad.'\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am more sad, because I am sad for souls,\\\" theFull Housealum said.\", \"from\": 3779, \"to\": 3850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I pray for my heart to break over what breaks God's heart.\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 3911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I just think about all the people that have rejected the Gospel of Jesus Christ or do not know the Gospel of Jesus Christ.\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 4038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And in the Bible in Galatians (6:7-8) it says, 'God is not mocked.\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4059, \"end\": 4068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epistle_to_the_Galatians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.893056349000852e-26, \"text\": \"Galatians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epistle_to_the_Galatians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epistle_to_the_Galatians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For whatever a person sows he will also reap.\", \"from\": 4106, \"to\": 4151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because the one who sows to his flesh will reap destruction from the flesh.\", \"from\": 4152, \"to\": 4227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the one who sows to the spirit will reap eternal life from the spirit.'\\\"\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bure ended her message by encouraging her 5.7 million followers to keep \\\"sharing the gospel.\\\"\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do not get tired of doing good.\", \"from\": 4401, \"to\": 4433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Keep sharing the gospel.\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's not just for the people that like openly mock God.\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is so many people - there is Christians out there that say, 'Well I am a Christian, it did not really bother me.'\", \"from\": 4519, \"to\": 4638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4554, \"end\": 4564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9985730195436575, \"rank\": 0.0014028534670267629, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 4598, \"end\": 4607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031347434765, \"rank\": 9.687464026184058e-05, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those people need to hear the gospel too.\", \"from\": 4639, \"to\": 4680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the ones that are lukewarm about it that may think like, 'Ah - I do not want to ruffle any feathers.\", \"from\": 4681, \"to\": 4786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Live and let live.\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let people do what they want.\", \"from\": 4806, \"to\": 4835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just gonna stay in my corner and be quiet about it.'\\\"\", \"from\": 4836, \"to\": 4894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Hallmark star stopped short of calling for a boycott.\", \"from\": 4896, \"to\": 4957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4904, \"end\": 4912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hallmark_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999999895444489, \"rank\": 1.0449577660078318e-08, \"text\": \"Hallmark\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hallmark_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hallmark_Channel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are a lot of great Christian athletes competing as well, but I want to cheer them on.\", \"from\": 4959, \"to\": 5051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4985, \"end\": 4994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999031347434765, \"rank\": 9.687464026184058e-05, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to see God getting the glory.\", \"from\": 5052, \"to\": 5088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am gonna watch,\\\" she said, noting that athletes \\\"had nothing to do with that opening ceremony,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 5089, \"to\": 5200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"FormerBiggest Losertrainer Jillian Michaels also slammed the act, writing on X: \\\"Dear fellow gays\\u2026 We demand tolerance and respect but then make a mockery of something sacred for over 2 billion Christians.\", \"from\": 5202, \"to\": 5407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5229, \"end\": 5245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jillian_Michaels\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jillian Michaels\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jillian_Michaels\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jillian_Michaels\"}, {\"begin\": 5396, \"end\": 5406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9985730195436575, \"rank\": 0.0014028534670267629, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This type of hypocrisy and lack of understanding is a bad look.\", \"from\": 5408, \"to\": 5471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We get outraged when the extreme right bashes us, but then we do this s-.\", \"from\": 5472, \"to\": 5545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What kind of reaction do you think they will have toward the LGBTQ+ community after this.\", \"from\": 5546, \"to\": 5635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is NOT how we break down barriers it's how you build them.\\\"\", \"from\": 5636, \"to\": 5700, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The drag performance also drew the ire ofPiers Morganwho wrote on X: \\\"A drag queen mockery of the Last Supper at the Olympics?\", \"from\": 5702, \"to\": 5828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Would they have mocked any other religion like this?\", \"from\": 5829, \"to\": 5881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Appalling decision.\\\"\", \"from\": 5882, \"to\": 5902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Btw, what the f*ck was all this about?\", \"from\": 5904, \"to\": 5942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A drag queen mockery of the Last Supper at the Olympics?\", \"from\": 5943, \"to\": 5999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Would they have mocked any other religion like this?\", \"from\": 6000, \"to\": 6052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Appalling decision.pic.twitter.com/50uREKJEJd  Meanwhile, Donald Trump Jr. re-posted a photo of the depiction, saying, \\\"They are not even pretending anymore,\\\" while billionaire SpaceX, Tesla and X owner Elon Musk called the parody \\\"extremely disrespectful to Christians.\\\"\", \"from\": 6053, \"to\": 6324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6111, \"end\": 6127, \"titl